HEADWORD: Membership
<hw>Mem"ber*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state of being
a member.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The collective body of members, as of a
society.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Membral</ent>⟦br⟧
